We'll Shoot It Out Now-Hombre! DRAW Before I Drill You!
Mexican outlaw Zanti killed John Tobin's parents. John teams up with Dusty, also hurt by Zanti, to get the bad guy.

Original title: The Lawless Frontier (1934)

Genre: Colorized, Classics, Western
